nodes.text: D'nisenz was a dejarik player as of 22 BBY. In 22 BBY he participated in the Colonies Region dejarik championship, and witnessed a brawl between two other players, Ohh Bronna and Corwin Kaezeb. D'nisenz continued his quarterfinals match with Garem Will as the fight escalated, not noticing the mayhem until their board flickered off. Due to a lack of established protocol for such occurrences, D'nisenz was declared Colonies Region dejarik champion.
